  <h3 class='section-heading'>Search based on &quotOIDs&quot or &quotIDs&quot</h3>

  <ol>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/projectblacklight/blacklight/wiki#blacklight-configuration">Configure Blacklight</a></li>
  </ol>
